body:
Successfully builds on Ubuntu 20.04 with Python 3.7.7 and GCC 9.3.0 (via WSL)

https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/releases/tag/v2.3.0

@aweits I had to disable the change made in #16258 in order to get this to compile. I'll post the exact error message soon. We should figure this out before merging this PR.

Depends on #17735
